0: SELECT MAX(`Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)`) FROM frpm WHERE `County Name` = 'Alameda';	----- bird -----	california_schools
1: SELECT `School Name`, `Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)` FROM frpm JOIN satscores ON frpm.CDSCode = satscores.cds JOIN schools ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE `District Type` = 'Continuation High School' AND rtype = 'S' AND `Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)` IS NOT NULL ORDER BY `Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)` ASC LIMIT 3;	----- bird -----	california_schools
2: SELECT Zip FROM schools WHERE County = 'Fresno' AND Charter = 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
3: SELECT MailStreet || ' ' || MailCity || ' ' || MailState || ' ' || MailZip FROM schools WHERE CDSCode = (SELECT CDSCode FROM frpm ORDER BY `FRPM Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 1);	----- bird -----	california_schools
4: SELECT Phone FROM schools WHERE Charter = 1 AND OpenDate > '2000-01-01';	----- bird -----	california_schools
5: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools WHERE CDSCode IN (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE AvgScrMath < 400) AND Virtual = 'Yes';	----- bird -----	california_schools
6: SELECT schools.School FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE satscores.NumTstTakr > 500 AND (schools.Magnet = 1 OR schools.GSoffered LIKE '%Magnet%');	----- bird -----	california_schools
7: SELECT schools.Phone FROM schools JOIN satscores ON schools.CDSCode = satscores.cds WHERE satscores.NumTstTakr > 0 AND satscores.NumGE1500 > 0 ORDER BY satscores.NumTstTakr DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
8: SELECT SUM(NumTstTakr) FROM satscores WHERE cds IN (SELECT CDSCode FROM frpm ORDER BY `FRPM Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 1);	----- bird -----	california_schools
9: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM schools WHERE CDSCode IN (SELECT cds FROM satscores WHERE AvgScrMath > 560) AND FundingType = 'Charter';	----- bird -----	california_schools
